<h2>The 8 adaptation challenges</h2>
<p>Pick one. Each challenge has natural cross-references to other units in the year arc — pick a challenge you might want to carry into U5 (Hydrosphere), U6 (Biosphere + Land Use), or U7 (Energy) if it interests you.</p>

